    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to get this gorgeous ride into the hands of someone who will love it as much as I have. It is in truly stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with its care, so it\u2019s running beautifully and is sparkling clean inside and out. It\u2019s a total dream to drive, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to fall in love with it the moment you see it. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
