    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks, feels, and smells as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been obsessively maintained in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen a drop of rain. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will not find a single rock chip, swirl mark, or blemish on its surface. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of untouched luxury. The premium leather seats remain firm and entirely uncreased, while the high-gloss trim pieces still retain their factory-fresh clarity. Every button, switch, and technological feature operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized dealerships\u2014all service records are organized and included. With incredibly low mileage and a spotless undercarriage, this is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection without compromise.",
